ActCanada Council for the Arts Act
PrecisAppointment of JAN-FRYDERYK PLESZCZYNSKI of Montréal, Quebec, to be a member of the Canada Council for the Arts, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Jennifer Dorner, whose term will expire, effective August 4, 2023.
